Jack Larson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Larson 0 For the textile designer, see Jack Lenor LarsenJack Edward Larson (February 8, 1928 – September 20, 2015) was an American actor, librettist, screenwriter and producer best known for his portrayal of photographer/cub reporter Jimmy Olsen on the television series Adventures of Superman.
